Spain’s Opposition Leader Rajoy Says Would Be Risky to Raise VAT

-- B y   E m m a   R o s s - T h o m a s
-- 
2011-09-19T07:25:21Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-19/spain-s-opposition-leader-rajoy-says-would-be-risky-to-raise-vat.html
Spanish opposition leader  Mariano
Rajoy  said it would be “risky” to increase the rate of value-
added tax now, as consumer spending remains weak. He spoke in an
interview with Cadena Ser today.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Emma Ross-Thomas at 
 erossthomas@bloomberg.net  